title: $:/plugins/tg/layout/css-units

<br>

* You can enter values in allowed CSS units, e.g. `%`, `px`, `em`, ...
* You can enter colors:
** by name, e.g. `red`, `blue`, ... see [[w3schools|https://www.w3schools.com/tags/ref_colornames.asp]]
** as 6 (sometimes 3) digit Hex color code, e.g. `#FF0000` (or `#F00`)
** with the color macro, e.g. `<<colour primary>>`.
